organizations.name: jordan brand reveals its tonal air jordan

text:
Model: Air Jordan 1 Retro 
Key Features: Tonal all-suede upper, corresponding tonal midsoles to match. 
Release Date: Spring 2017 
Price: Unknown 
Availability: Unknown 
Editor’s Notes: The suede upper is a dramatic departure from the Air Jordan 1’s classic leather makeup, and it’ll be interesting to see how it plays out in terms of demand. As for the red version specifically, all-red sneakers have typically been met with positive reception, so that trend will likely continue with this Jordan release.
